# Auth Pages — iBot-Inspired Flat Design

All auth pages follow the same split-screen layout inspired by iBot (ibot-chat.com/user/login.php).

## Layout Structure

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Decorative gradient circles (absolute, subtle)  │
├────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┤
│   Product Info     │      Form Area             │
│   (white bg)       │      (#f6f7fb bg)          │
│                    │                            │
│   ⚡ Logo (float)  │      Heading               │
│   Heading          │      Subheading            │
│   Subheading       │      Form fields           │
│   3 Features       │      CTA button            │
│   w/ colored icons │      Links                 │
│                    │                            │
│   (lg:flex, hidden │      (always visible)      │
│    on mobile)      │                            │
└────────────────────┴────────────────────────────┘
```

## Design Tokens

- Page background: `#f6f7fb`
- Info panel: white (`bg-white`)
- Border color: `#d0d4e4` (inputs, cards)
- Input radius: `rounded-xl` (NOT `rounded-full`)
- Button radius: `rounded-xl`
- Focus ring: `focus:border-ocean focus:ring-[3px] focus:ring-ocean/10`
- Input padding: `py-3 pr-4 pl-11` (with left icon)
- Shadows: `shadow-[0_4px_20px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)]`

## Decorative Circles

Subtle gradient circles positioned at page corners and inside the white panel:
- Background circles: `from-ocean/5 to-purple-500/5`, `from-emerald-500/5 to-amber-500/5`
- Panel circles: `from-ocean/[0.04] to-sky-300/[0.06]`, `from-emerald-400/[0.03] to-amber-300/[0.04]`
- All circles: `pointer-events-none absolute rounded-full`

## Feature Icons

Three features with colored circle icons:
- Emerald: `bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500`
- Purple: `bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-500`
- Amber: `bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-500`

## Input Fields

Icons on the LEFT (in visual terms), using absolute positioning:
```tsx
<div className="relative">
  <input className="... py-3 pr-4 pl-11 ..." />
  <div className="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3">
    <Icon className="h-[18px] w-[18px] text-slate-400" />
  </div>
</div>
```

## Copy Guidelines

Feature text must match homepage messaging:
- עורך ויזואלי מלא
- דומיין מותאם אישי
- ניהול לידים מובנה

## Auth Flow Pages

| Route | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `/login` | Email + password login, "שכחת סיסמה?" link |
| `/register` | 3-step wizard: details → template → creating |
| `/forgot-password` | Email input → sends reset link via Resend |
| `/reset-password?token=...` | New password + confirm → redirect to login with success |
| `/logout` | GET route → destroys session → redirect to login |

## Animations

- Logo icon: `animate-[float_3s_ease-in-out_infinite]` (defined in globals.css)
- Button hover: `hover:scale-[1.02]`
- Input focus: smooth ring transition via `transition-all duration-200`
